>>ARDAGH: Yeah.

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:43.540 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you train people
to become awakening coaches.

00:17:43.540 --> 00:17:44.802 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Yes.

00:17:44.802 --> 00:17:46.260 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And--
because how long have

00:17:46.260 --> 00:17:49.990 align:middle line:84%
