people in awakening?

00:17:49.990 --> 00:17:51.790 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Oh, I
don't know, 25 years?

00:17:51.790 --> 00:17:53.040 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: 25 years.

00:17:53.040 --> 00:17:57.220 align:middle line:84%
So I want to ask you,
how do you train somebody

00:17:57.220 --> 00:17:59.539 align:middle line:90%
