00:17:59.539 --> 00:18:01.830 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Well, that's a
really good question, you see.

00:18:01.830 --> 00:18:04.246 align:middle line:84%
And if you don't mind, I'd
like to answer it in a slightly

00:18:04.246 --> 00:18:07.280 align:middle line:84%
