part of a bigger question.

00:18:07.280 --> 00:18:16.760 align:middle line:84%
So I think that the most
eternal longing and quest

00:18:16.760 --> 00:18:19.380 align:middle line:84%
that human beings
have is to come home.

00:18:19.380 --> 00:18:19.880 align:middle line:90%
All right?

00:18:19.880 --> 00:18:22.980 align:middle line:90%


00:18:22.980 --> 00:18:27.934 align:middle line:84%
I would say that that's
the first conscious human

00:18:27.934 --> 00:18:29.600 align:middle line:84%
being-- if there was
such a thing-- that

00:18:29.600 --> 00:18:32.170 align:middle line:84%
was the fir-- that
has always been there.

00:18:32.170 --> 00:18:34.040 align:middle line:90%
This longing to come home.

00:18:34.040 --> 00:18:36.790 align:middle line:84%
And we have an intuition
for what home is.

00:18:36.790 --> 00:18:38.570 align:middle line:84%
So when we're talking
about awakening,

00:18:38.570 --> 00:18:42.900 align:middle line:84%
we're talking about a very,
very core, intuitive longing

00:18:42.900 --> 00:18:46.160 align:middle line:90%
that is present in everybody.

00:18:46.160 --> 00:18:49.970 align:middle line:84%
Now this is all part of kind
of the historical development

00:18:49.970 --> 00:18:53.060 align:middle line:90%
of the last thousands of years.

00:18:53.060 --> 00:18:57.180 align:middle line:84%
Like many, many,
many things in life,

00:18:57.180 --> 00:19:00.055 align:middle line:84%
awakening has been
somewhat co-opted

00:19:00.055 --> 00:19:02.920 align:middle line:84%
by the domination
of masculine energy.

00:19:02.920 --> 00:19:04.150 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:19:04.150 --> 00:19:05.940 align:middle line:84%
So lots of things
in life have been

00:19:05.940 --> 00:19:08.646 align:middle line:90%
dominated by the masculine.

00:19:08.646 --> 00:19:09.520 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Historically.

00:19:09.520 --> 00:19:10.144 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Yeah.

00:19:10.144 --> 00:19:11.610 align:middle line:90%
I don't necessarily mean by men.

00:19:11.610 --> 00:19:12.736 align:middle line:90%
I mean by masculine energy.

00:19:12.736 --> 00:19:13.318 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:19:13.318 --> 00:19:15.600 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So, for example,
international relations

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:17.120 align:middle line:84%
over the last
thousands of years has

00:19:17.120 --> 00:19:18.490 align:middle line:84%
been dominated by
masculine energy,

00:19:18.490 --> 00:19:20.031 align:middle line:84%
so we've had more
of a tendency to go

00:19:20.031 --> 00:19:22.380 align:middle line:84%
to war, which is a
masculine preoccupation,

00:19:22.380 --> 00:19:24.220 align:middle line:90%
than towards diplomacy.

