Or business has been very much
dominated by the masculine.

00:19:27.320 --> 00:19:29.820 align:middle line:84%
So we had a very competitive,
testosterone-driven business

00:19:29.820 --> 00:19:30.320 align:middle line:90%
environment.

00:19:30.320 --> 00:19:31.140 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: These are the
things I was thinking

00:19:31.140 --> 00:19:32.765 align:middle line:84%
of when we were
talking about the ego.

00:19:32.765 --> 00:19:33.240 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Yeah.

