testosterone-driven behavior.

00:19:39.617 --> 00:19:40.450 align:middle line:90%
It's just a hormone.

00:19:40.450 --> 00:19:43.270 align:middle line:84%
And it's a good
hormone in many ways.

00:19:43.270 --> 00:19:46.650 align:middle line:84%
Spiritual awakening has
also been very much co-opted

00:19:46.650 --> 00:19:48.180 align:middle line:90%
by the masculine.

00:19:48.180 --> 00:19:48.790 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:19:48.790 --> 00:19:52.770 align:middle line:84%
Which means that we
have made awakening

00:19:52.770 --> 00:19:56.010 align:middle line:90%
into the idea of a journey.

00:19:56.010 --> 00:19:58.210 align:middle line:90%
A journey on a path.

00:19:58.210 --> 00:20:00.240 align:middle line:84%
Now you're on this
path and you're

00:20:00.240 --> 00:20:01.460 align:middle line:90%
working toward this goal.

00:20:01.460 --> 00:20:04.700 align:middle line:84%
And that's basically how
the masculine psyche works.

00:20:04.700 --> 00:20:06.789 align:middle line:84%
The masculine psyche
likes to think of a goal--

00:20:06.789 --> 00:20:07.580 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Conquering.

00:20:07.580 --> 00:20:09.671 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: --and likes to
have difficult obstacles

00:20:09.671 --> 00:20:10.170 align:middle line:90%
to overcome.

00:20:10.170 --> 00:20:11.020 align:middle line:90%
The hero's journey.

00:20:11.020 --> 00:20:13.145 align:middle line:84%
You break through the
obstacles to get to the goal.

00:20:13.145 --> 00:20:13.719 align:middle line:90%
Right?

00:20:13.719 --> 00:20:14.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:20:14.260 --> 00:20:17.680 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So that's what the
masculine does with everything.

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:21.460 align:middle line:84%
So for thousands of
years, man or woman,

00:20:21.460 --> 00:20:23.080 align:middle line:84%
if you were interested
in awakening,

00:20:23.080 --> 00:20:27.030 align:middle line:84%
what was mostly available to
you was a hierarchical context--

00:20:27.030 --> 00:20:30.980 align:middle line:84%
very often with a teacher who
was reported to be enlightened,

00:20:30.980 --> 00:20:35.250 align:middle line:84%
which is a concept
we could question.

00:20:35.250 --> 00:20:37.190 align:middle line:84%
Then you would join
an organization,

00:20:37.190 --> 00:20:39.612 align:middle line:84%
follow very often a
holy book of dogma.

00:20:39.612 --> 00:20:40.945 align:middle line:90%
And this was what was available.

00:20:40.945 --> 00:20:45.350 align:middle line:84%
I mean, either you really
were just like a free agent

00:20:45.350 --> 00:20:48.150 align:middle line:84%
who winged it on their own-- but
that was a very difficult thing

00:20:48.150 --> 00:20:49.617 align:middle line:84%
to do-- or if you
wanted help, this

00:20:49.617 --> 00:20:50.950 align:middle line:90%
was the help that was available.

00:20:50.950 --> 00:20:55.310 align:middle line:84%
Very, very patriarchal,
structured help.

00:20:55.310 --> 00:21:02.440 align:middle line:84%
Well, even 30, 40 years ago,
this remained unquestioned.

00:21:02.440 --> 00:21:06.740 align:middle line:84%
If we go back to when you and
I were discovering this stuff,

00:21:06.740 --> 00:21:07.920 align:middle line:90%
that was the way it was.

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:13.380 align:middle line:84%
People went to Maharishi Mahesh
Yogi with TM or to Rajneesh

00:21:13.380 --> 00:21:15.574 align:middle line:90%
or-- he's now Osho.

00:21:15.574 --> 00:21:16.740 align:middle line:90%
That was what was available.

00:21:16.740 --> 00:21:19.430 align:middle line:84%
You went to a male teacher
with an organization

00:21:19.430 --> 00:21:22.540 align:middle line:84%
and you would fit in
with what was going on.

00:21:22.540 --> 00:21:26.920 align:middle line:90%


00:21:26.920 --> 00:21:31.560 align:middle line:84%
My teacher, Poonja Ji,
did not operate that way.

00:21:31.560 --> 00:21:33.270 align:middle line:90%
He was more of a coach.

00:21:33.270 --> 00:21:34.790 align:middle line:90%
He didn't have an organization.

00:21:34.790 --> 00:21:35.910 align:middle line:90%
He didn't have a teaching.

00:21:35.910 --> 00:21:38.450 align:middle line:84%
And as quickly as possible,
he entered into a friendship

00:21:38.450 --> 00:21:40.627 align:middle line:84%
with people that was
non-hierarchical.

00:21:40.627 --> 00:21:42.210 align:middle line:84%
And that was really
what I grew up on.

00:21:42.210 --> 00:21:46.090 align:middle line:90%
That was what worked for me.

00:21:46.090 --> 00:21:51.040 align:middle line:84%
But once I got back
to America again,

00:21:51.040 --> 00:21:53.080 align:middle line:90%
initially he asked me to teach.

00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:55.710 align:middle line:84%
He said, OK, now
you know the secret.

00:21:55.710 --> 00:21:59.490 align:middle line:84%
Go and share the secret
with your friends.

00:21:59.490 --> 00:22:01.420 align:middle line:90%
So that's what happened.

00:22:01.420 --> 00:22:03.840 align:middle line:84%
But very quickly the
same thing occurred.

00:22:03.840 --> 00:22:05.650 align:middle line:84%
But now it was
ridiculous because I'd

00:22:05.650 --> 00:22:07.950 align:middle line:84%
been 20 years on
the receiving end

00:22:07.950 --> 00:22:09.640 align:middle line:84%
of this hierarchical
relationship,

00:22:09.640 --> 00:22:12.000 align:middle line:84%
now I found myself on
the other side of it,

00:22:12.000 --> 00:22:14.390 align:middle line:84%
that I was sitting
in a chair and people

00:22:14.390 --> 00:22:17.970 align:middle line:84%
would sit there
and like, namaste.

00:22:17.970 --> 00:22:18.850 align:middle line:90%
Oh, he looked at me.

00:22:18.850 --> 00:22:19.760 align:middle line:90%
Wow.

00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.630 align:middle line:90%
And I realized it's all made up.

00:22:21.630 --> 00:22:23.340 align:middle line:90%
A lot of it is projection.

00:22:23.340 --> 00:22:25.650 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: What we're looking
for, yes, essentially.

00:22:25.650 --> 00:22:26.890 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: The whole
theater, you see,

00:22:26.890 --> 00:22:28.723 align:middle line:84%
the whole theater of a
teacher and students.

00:22:28.723 --> 00:22:30.840 align:middle line:84%
A tremendous amount
of projection happens.

00:22:30.840 --> 00:22:36.320 align:middle line:84%
So after a few years-- three,
four years of doing this-- I

00:22:36.320 --> 00:22:39.086 align:middle line:84%
went back to see him
again-- my teacher.

00:22:39.086 --> 00:22:41.210 align:middle line:84%
And I said to him, I don't
want to do this anymore.

00:22:41.210 --> 00:22:43.090 align:middle line:84%
I don't want to be
a teacher because it

00:22:43.090 --> 00:22:45.880 align:middle line:84%
feels to me a very artificial
kind of theater is created.

00:22:45.880 --> 00:22:46.630 align:middle line:90%
And it's not true.

00:22:46.630 --> 00:22:48.090 align:middle line:90%
This hierarchy is not true.

00:22:48.090 --> 00:22:50.590 align:middle line:84%
To say somebody's enlightened
and somebody's un-enlightened,

00:22:50.590 --> 00:22:53.240 align:middle line:90%
it's just not true.

00:22:53.240 --> 00:22:55.887 align:middle line:84%
If we were talking about
looking at the sky,

00:22:55.887 --> 00:22:57.345 align:middle line:84%
we wouldn't then
make a demarcation

00:22:57.345 --> 00:22:59.570 align:middle line:84%
and say, oh, this
is a sky see-er,

00:22:59.570 --> 00:23:01.340 align:middle line:90%
this is a non sky see-er.

00:23:01.340 --> 00:23:02.937 align:middle line:90%
It's just the sky.

00:23:02.937 --> 00:23:03.520 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

00:23:03.520 --> 00:23:05.186 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So seeing
the truth of things,

00:23:05.186 --> 00:23:09.870 align:middle line:84%
it doesn't make you a
different kind of human being,

00:23:09.870 --> 00:23:12.120 align:middle line:84%
it's something that's
available to everybody.

00:23:12.120 --> 00:23:15.160 align:middle line:84%
So I said to him, I just wasn't
comfortable with the theater

00:23:15.160 --> 00:23:16.884 align:middle line:84%
that was easily
created around it.

00:23:16.884 --> 00:23:18.550 align:middle line:84%
His response to me
was very interesting.

00:23:18.550 --> 00:23:21.780 align:middle line:90%
He said, do whatever you want.

00:23:21.780 --> 00:23:25.077 align:middle line:84%
Except, of course, he said,
(GRUFFLY) do whatever you want.

00:23:25.077 --> 00:23:26.660 align:middle line:84%
(NORMAL VOICE) But
you have a destiny,

00:23:26.660 --> 00:23:29.610 align:middle line:84%
and the destiny
eventually will win.

00:23:29.610 --> 00:23:30.330 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:23:30.330 --> 00:23:32.246 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: I didn't know
what he meant by that.

00:23:32.246 --> 00:23:33.810 align:middle line:90%
But I said, OK.

00:23:33.810 --> 00:23:36.012 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That was very
good advice, though.

00:23:36.012 --> 00:23:37.845 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Well, I had
no idea what he meant.

00:23:37.845 --> 00:23:38.460 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:23:38.460 --> 00:23:40.640 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So I went
back to America,

00:23:40.640 --> 00:23:42.660 align:middle line:84%
and now I had nothing
to do because I

00:23:42.660 --> 00:23:44.840 align:middle line:90%
