00:24:13.970 --> 00:24:16.550 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And that is-- so
you're living your destiny.

00:24:16.550 --> 00:24:18.030 align:middle line:90%
You're living out your destiny.

00:24:18.030 --> 00:24:19.470 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: But I didn't know
what it was then, you see?

00:24:19.470 --> 00:24:19.670 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Wow.

00:24:19.670 --> 00:24:20.740 align:middle line:84%
That's a beautiful
example though.

00:24:20.740 --> 00:24:21.990 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Didn't
know what it was.

00:24:21.990 --> 00:24:23.050 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: In Arjuna's
eighth book--

00:24:23.050 --> 00:24:24.280 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Let me
say one more thing.

00:24:24.280 --> 00:24:24.720 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Oh, yes.

