moment of awakening,

00:29:56.540 --> 00:29:58.740 align:middle line:84%
which is also always
somehow a moment--

00:29:58.740 --> 00:30:00.390 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you
can have several.

00:30:00.390 --> 00:30:01.400 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Oh, yeah.

00:30:01.400 --> 00:30:02.000 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

00:30:02.000 --> 00:30:03.380 align:middle line:84%
You can have now
and now and now.

00:30:03.380 --> 00:30:03.880 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:30:03.880 --> 00:30:06.046 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So whenever there's
a moment of awakening,

00:30:06.046 --> 00:30:10.000 align:middle line:84%
