00:30:50.425 --> 00:30:52.383 align:middle line:84%
in the same way; it's
the same original nature.

00:30:52.383 --> 00:30:53.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Through their filters.

00:30:53.290 --> 00:30:54.860 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Well, not just
through conditioning.

00:30:54.860 --> 00:30:56.610 align:middle line:84%
It's the same original
nature, but there's

00:30:56.610 --> 00:31:00.760 align:middle line:84%
like you could say there's a
unique flavor to each human

00:31:00.760 --> 00:31:01.730 align:middle line:90%
