00:31:11.265 --> 00:31:14.430 align:middle line:84%
a unique natural character
they bring into the world.

00:31:14.430 --> 00:31:15.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:31:15.640 --> 00:31:18.820 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Well, so we understand
that, that your original nature

00:31:18.820 --> 00:31:22.340 align:middle line:84%
is going to express differently
through different physical

00:31:22.340 --> 00:31:23.890 align:middle line:90%
