00:31:23.890 --> 00:31:27.570 align:middle line:84%
Well, the most fundamental
difference between people,

00:31:27.570 --> 00:31:31.180 align:middle line:84%
the first thing you notice about
anybody before anything else,

00:31:31.180 --> 00:31:32.870 align:middle line:90%
