color a little bit?

00:31:36.680 --> 00:31:38.106 align:middle line:90%
That would be understandable.

00:31:38.106 --> 00:31:39.730 align:middle line:84%
If I said, well, I
thought I remembered

00:31:39.730 --> 00:31:40.980 align:middle line:90%
you being a bit taller.

00:31:40.980 --> 00:31:42.480 align:middle line:90%
That be understandable.

00:31:42.480 --> 00:31:45.252 align:middle line:84%
If I said, oh, Lisa, I thought
I remembered you had glasses.

00:31:45.252 --> 00:31:46.460 align:middle line:90%
That would be understandable.

00:31:46.460 --> 00:31:47.756 align:middle line:84%
If I said, oh, Lisa,
nice to see you.

00:31:47.756 --> 00:31:48.906 align:middle line:90%
Funny, I thought you were a man.

00:31:48.906 --> 00:31:50.510 align:middle line:84%
That would be
completely weird, right?

00:31:50.510 --> 00:31:52.876 align:middle line:84%
Nobody ever mistakes
somebody's gender.

00:31:52.876 --> 00:31:53.750 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This is true.

00:31:53.750 --> 00:31:55.310 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: Other things
you can get mixed up.

00:31:55.310 --> 00:31:57.510 align:middle line:84%
You could say to me, I didn't
remember you had a beard.

00:31:57.510 --> 00:31:57.880 align:middle line:90%
I would get that.

00:31:57.880 --> 00:31:59.060 align:middle line:84%
But if you said,
Arjuna, I thought

00:31:59.060 --> 00:32:00.726 align:middle line:84%
you were a woman,
that would-- I would--

00:32:00.726 --> 00:32:02.393 align:middle line:84%
So gender is the most
fundamental thing.

00:32:02.393 --> 00:32:04.642 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I don't know, you
could be pretty transgender.

00:32:04.642 --> 00:32:05.612 align:middle line:90%
You're pretty neutral.

00:32:05.612 --> 00:32:06.820 align:middle line:90%
>>ARDAGH: Let's not go there.

00:32:06.820 --> 00:32:07.319 align:middle line:90%
Anyway.

00:32:07.319 --> 00:32:09.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You're gender neutral.

00:32:09.070 --> 00:32:11.470 align:middle line:84%
>>ARDAGH: So gender is the
most fundamental distinction

00:32:11.470 --> 00:32:11.970 align:middle line:90%
we make.

00:32:11.970 --> 00:32:15.540 align:middle line:84%
Yet, despite the fact that
that's the most fundamental

00:32:15.540 --> 00:32:20.190 align:middle line:84%
distinction, we have actually
made very little distinction

00:32:20.190 --> 00:32:22.590 align:middle line:84%
